title: Off Grid Cabin in the Woods...Spring trip ...massive snow

media:group.media:title: Off Grid Cabin in the Woods...Spring trip ...massive snow
media:group.media:description:
It's springtime....but up at the Off grid cabin there is still three feet of snow. In this video Brooke and I snowmobile into our remote off grid cabin to see how things made it through the winter. We also want to do some snow shoeing, and walk the property one last time before breakup when the snow falls apart.
If you want to see Brooke's version of this trip check it out at her channel "girl in the woods" here's the link. 
              https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zE-ukurL_7k&t=569s
